Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:47.83,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.18,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:53.55,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:02:00.25,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:08.07,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:15.47,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:22.04,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:30.28,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.19,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.80,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:38.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:44.49,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:49.63,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:53.68,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:03:00.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------INCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.69,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}纷纷雪花 是星星的碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.88,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}将手伸向天体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.95,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}你也感受到那交错的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:53.49,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,600)\blur4}此刻一切都在黑白之间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.85,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}悄悄溢出的白色气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:18.02,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}那是心中话语的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:22.14,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是那一点点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:26.72,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}让天空撒下一线光明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:30.67,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}悲痛伤感沾湿的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.57,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}为保持纯白重新合上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:42.87,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,500)\blur4}我有去面对未来那种温柔的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.37,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}在谁都不知道的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:51.57,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}等待黎明的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.37,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}给我带来了光的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:59.74,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}从明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.99,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}纷纷雪花 是星星的碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.18,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}将手伸向天体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:12.25,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}你也相信那交错的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:21.79,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,600)\blur4}此刻一切都在黑白之间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:37.52,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}冰封的记忆开始融化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.42,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}与手中紧握的爱一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:49.72,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,500)\blur4}转身便能感觉到青空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:54.22,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}虽然是各走各自的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:58.42,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}但依然会有相遇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.22,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}安静地入睡  梦境里的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:11.84,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,600)\blur4}此刻一切仍在黑白之间
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:33.50,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}当两人漂移不定的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}相互触碰之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:42.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻 你在想着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:48.11,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:50.01,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:56.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:03.67,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:11.69,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:15.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.72,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.15,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:22.63,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:29.70,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Feel my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.30,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}在你坦然露出笑容的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:40.85,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:44.65,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}会让我的泪水更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:50.05,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}You are my only shooting star
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 拓人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和子好像请假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君也没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人同学有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君明知可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是驯化了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…到！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答刚才的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没听课
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课东张西望也要适可而止哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到王之柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第2队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代代表海德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团总会 现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如各位所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚王之柱贯穿了本岛的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方驯化了素体Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这种事态的第3队九重葛责任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是一直处于可以驯化的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧发生在昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就成了我们九重葛的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是他现在的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据遗留记录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh过去所有的驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在使王之柱出现后再也没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是形同死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者已经断了气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有必要确认进藤须方的当前状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若Samekh的驾驭者觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绮罗星十字团也必须考虑相应对策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若与之为敌会很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 也算是沉醉的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就让九重葛来负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要负责到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟他打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 尽情展现你拿手的游泳本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是对他们抱有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天社团活动休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 只是听到声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是单人戏剧的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯咖啡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子似乎从天亮前就在海湾独自净身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在祈祷须方君能醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好友三人组之一待在这里没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心须方 也担心和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然担心…可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 现在我还能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两人和一人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕你已无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是他们俩的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们认识的时间更长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们背负着无法想象的沉重命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能获得幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我无法想象他们真正获得幸福的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所背负的问题都无法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 自从你来到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你和他们俩和睦相处三人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的 觉得让他们幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你们好友三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开心的笑容之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始有了这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来干大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 讴歌青春对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你们让我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子似乎很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有拓人这样的人出现在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能为他们俩做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是陪在身边也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望朋友陪在身边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会有不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他们来说你就是这种朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们不这么希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的灵魂也一定在渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人都很笨拙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是孤岛长大的乡下人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是和子的祖母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tau的印记是几时继承的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子在海湾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
