Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在这里就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化「柱」后 还一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的重赛 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…须方他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要清除外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的遗迹全部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这些人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chesuto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游弋吧 美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下潜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸裂 Tau银河光线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会又失控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成这样想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间里 须方醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去大屋找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得马上去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王宣布让出王位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王最初就打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:18:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把王位让给带来青色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是萨姆拒绝接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王 我只想要您的银河之船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐它 迈上驶往璀璨银河的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要什么王位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无意拥有什么国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到鱼妹妹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王则说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 会给你任何想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦无意违背诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那艘银河之船让于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺客萨姆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想开动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你须将恋爱中少女的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴不剩 注入它的引擎中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 必须杀死恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则无法开动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起它是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊 这糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为恭迎您加入我们绮罗星十字团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此前来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第一队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王之座 为你空缺已久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让银河美少年靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算用王之柱 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复平时的须方了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你打的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 想找死吗
